{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"Kecelakaanlah bagi setiap pengumpat lagi pencela,","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:2","price":"yang mengumpulkan harta dan menghitung-hitungnya1601,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1601.  Maksudnya mengumpulkan dan menghitung-hitung harta yang karenanya dia menjadikan kikir dan tidak mau menafkahkannya di jalan Allah Subḥānahu wa Ta‘ālā. ","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:3","price":"dia mengira bahwa hartanya itu dapat mengekalkannya,","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:4","price":"sekali-kali tidak! Sesungguhnya dia benar-benar akan dilemparkan ke dalam ῌuṭamah.","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:5","price":"Dan tahukah kamu apa ῌuṭamah itu?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6184,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:6","price":"(Yaitu) api (yang disediakan) Allah yang dinyalakan,","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6185,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:7","price":"yang (membakar) sampai ke hati.","arabic":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6186,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:8","price":"Sesungguhnya api itu ditutup rapat atas mereka,","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6187,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"104:9","price":"(sedang mereka itu) diikat pada tiang-tiang yang panjang.","arabic":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6188,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah","Chapter Al-Humazah","Humazah","Surah Humazah","Chapter Humazah","Al Humazah","Surah Al Humazah","Chapter Al Humazah","Surah 104","Chapter 104","The Traducer","الهمزة"]}